data.description: Welcome to this awesome 5 bed 3 bath home located in the great city of Surprise.  The perfect home for your family.  You can swim and BBQ with your gas fed grill or just hang out on the patio.  You are minutes from the Loop 303, close to shopping and entertainment.  This home also features smart home tech.  No need to buy a W/D or Fridge, it comes with it!  Master Bedroom is located on 1st floor along with a guest suite with bathroom.
